# TDD (Hard Rule)

- Red → green → refactor. Write a failing test first; then minimal code to pass; then refactor. No production code without a failing test that justifies it. Applies to pure functions, services, API routes, components; same for integration/E2E where practical. CI runs full suite; all pass.
